{"tid":2235777,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國史上最癲嘅儲物狂，「收藏品」估值至少100至400萬鎊","createTime":"2020-10-09T03:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T04:05:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1b01b5890e48b829cf7ba145c30e257649bba3","tid":2235777,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:10:09.000Z","msg":"Huge Nottingham 'hoarder' collection 'could fetch &pound;1m'<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-nottinghamshire-54463270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-nottinghamshire-54463270&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr94mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=8a8dc185\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-nottinghamshire-54463270&h=4e8651bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-nottinghamshire-54463270</a>"},{"pid":"cd07160c954618acd044459dcda4910dafd3ee88","tid":2235777,"uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"邊個話毒L剩係識儲垃圾？<br />\n英國史上最癲嘅儲物狂，「收藏品」估值至少100至400萬鎊<br />\n<br />\n英國Nottingham有一個單身獨居嘅電腦程式員，响廿年前開始唔無人知點解不停購物儲嘢，結果塞的自己間三房House，再租多一個一房Apartment，兩個車房，鄰居個Garden。係滿到上天花，門都開唔到嗰種，滿到自己臨死前要租B&amp;B住。<br />\n<br />\n更奇怪嘅係大部份嘅「收藏」寄到之後都係連包裹都唔開。到佢過身之後，佢阿哥就醒喇，搵拍賣行嘅人一齊睇下個細佬儲咗啲乜，開幾箱之後嚇到拍賣行儍咗...<br />\n<br />\n六萬件收藏包括邱吉爾、甘地、甘迺廸、貓王嘅親筆信，經典漫畫同珍藏限量唱片，古董書同報紙，相機，古董電器玩具，結他，首飾，太空人升空紀念品，古代軍事物品，諗唔到嘅都有，有啲仲要相同嘅都儲幾十件。最後拍賣行要搵18個員工，用咗四個星期開包裹再分類整理，然後用8個人3架車六個禮拜先清晒間屋。<br />\n<br />\n而拍賣行嘅老闆話入行50年都未見過咁巨型無主題嘅收藏系列，估計最終價值100至400萬鎊（底價都50萬鎊）。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，好明顯係一個病態儲物同購物狂，但係自問曾經都係一條毒L，聽過無數次身邊嘅人話「嘥晒啲錢，買買埋埋啲垃圾，阻住晒啲地方，珍乜藏吖，送都無人要呀！」，真正嘅價值根本未必係錢，但又有幾多人明白？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/153006095227869/posts/925149014680236/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F153006095227869%2Fposts%2F925149014680236%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr94mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=35feb484\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/153006095227869/posts/925149014680236/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"849faa158d47c2c2f179938f460cc64fd844bba6","tid":2235777,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d017e0a1cb51677efa52a1661f9a1fa77df6c9","tid":2235777,"uid":82717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"無主題收藏系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda7b9989d236b94c31d2ff8a50e41d549d8960c","tid":2235777,"uid":64636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"好誇張<br />\n仲要唔拆<br />\n如果佢有女就仆街"},{"pid":"c973cb383c9677ca1f0aa022f08c21603be51c40","tid":2235777,"uid":27568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"買太多拆都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實拆左會慳好多位<br />\n<br />\n但儲野好易一開始有主題<br />\n儲儲下覺得第d 野幾得意買埋<br />\n之後係咁變無主題"},{"pid":"63b1b5ccc20c2bb03f3ae7107289030c14d7f969","tid":2235777,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:24:32.000Z","msg":"奇貨可居"},{"pid":"eca86a91af1514e73bb8ba5b148803159575cb6d","tid":2235777,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"邱吉爾、甘地、甘迺廸、貓王嘅親筆信<br />\n<br />\n依D想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d75ede9599dbc6ef73ec3327fff38c6aa8aa0a6","tid":2235777,"uid":199602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"Auction Hunters<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad4902eaba5e5e24d74b56baad46d3e19beac46","tid":2235777,"uid":55956,